{ This chapter contains just a handful of variations I consider some of the best ones for your first glimpse into the world of the Caro-Kann.  You will recognize them when they arise later in the main chapters, often in more depth. Also note the main chapters contain more thorough descriptions of each major variation, including an overview outlining our setup and containing key ideas and popularity statistics.  So, use this Quickstarter Guide as a brief initiation before diving into the main chapters. When you're ready, it's best to begin your study with the Big 3: Exchange, Advance, and Classical / Two Knights.   Enjoy! }
