8... dxc4 9. Qxc4 Qd5
{ The queens will come off the board either this move or next @@StartBracket@@after  10.Qb3  Qxb3  @@EndBracket@@ after which our position is perfectly healthy.   Remember to recapture with the c-pawn! }
