14. Rad1
{ Keith Arkell LOVES the endgame. Do you remember how Keith transitioned into one from this position? }
14... Bg5
{ Black is encouraging as many trades as possible. This is especially effective when Whtie has the bishop pair. }
15. Bxg5 Qxg5 16. Re5 Qf6
{ Without queens on the board, Keith has the utmost confidence in his beloved Caro-Kann structure. }
