19. Re3
{ The queens are off the board and Keith's centre is strong as rocks. What is the plan now? }
19... b5
{ Now the endgame really begins, as well as Black's minority attack. The position is objectively equal, but because of Black's extra pawn presence in the centre, Keith has great practical chances, and he understands the minority attack better than almost anybody on the planet. Keith wants to arrange the ...b5-b4 break to soften the white pawns, but not just for the sake of it. The ultimate goal is to use the pawns in order to make the rooks as active as possible and give them purpose! }
